{"tid":1558974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【建政70年】教徒被迫唱紅歌祝福祖國 神學院長：港人實抗拒！","createTime":"2019-09-10T15:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T15:40:19.000Z","uid":279854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3bfcbddaff8b88ba251fac636920ea4182677fdd","tid":1558974,"uid":279854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:40:19.000Z","msg":"中共慶祝建政70周年之際，舉行規模空前的慶祝活動，經常報道中國宗教自由和人權狀況的網上雜誌《寒冬》（Bitter Winter）近日報道，全國各地教堂由8月開始，被迫參與各種形式的愛國活動。信徒批評，這是一場對基督教信仰的侵蝕。香港中文大學崇基學院神學院院長邢福增向《蘋果》記者表示，以前三自教會（官方認可的「自治、自養、自傳」的基督教教會）都會唱紅歌歌頌共產黨，而今年適逢建政70年，似乎當局要全面徹底執行下去；若然這股風氣帶來香港，香港教徒必然抗拒。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KongUmbrella/posts/1483346131803785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKongUmbrella%2Fposts%2F1483346131803785&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4UzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=dbd18bc8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KongUmbrella/posts/1483346131803785</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bitterwintertw.b-cdn.net/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/20190901-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE%E6%B4%BB%E5%8A%A8-S-CN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbitterwintertw.b-cdn.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F20190901-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AE%25AE%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258A%25A8-S-CN.jpg&h=d851ab1b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}